==應用==
本屬當中的八角的果實是中國菜和東南亞地區烹飪的調味料之一，也具有[[中藥|中藥]]用途。但目前本種最大的用途是用以提煉[[莽草酸|莽草酸]]，因莽草酸是抗流感藥物[[奧司他韋|奧司他韋]]的起始原料。<ref>Abrecht, S.; Harrington, P.; Iding, H.; Karpf, M.; Trussardi, R.; Wirz, B.; Zutter, U. Chimia '''2004''', 58, 621.</ref><ref>''New, Azide-Free Transformation of Epoxides into 1,2-Diamino Compounds: Synthesis of the Anti-Influenza Neuraminidase Inhibitor Oseltamivir Phosphate (Tamiflu)'' Martin Karpf and René Trussardi [[J._Org._Chem.|J. Org. Chem.]]; '''2001'''; 66(6) pp 2044 - 2051; (Article) {{DOI|10.1021/jo005702l}}.</ref>地楓皮則是[[廣西|廣西]]地區的特產中藥材。<ref name="cvh"/>日本莽草在日本也用作製作寺廟用的[[香|香]]。雖然外表相近，但本種的野生果實多含有劇毒，不宜食用。<ref name="JAPAN">{{cite web|url=http://pediatrics.aappublications.org/cgi/content/full/peds.2004-0058v1|title=Neurotoxicities in infants seen with the consumption of star anise tea|work=PEDIATRICS|accessdate=2010-08-09|date=2004-10-18|archive-date=2009-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090711225137/http://pediatrics.aappublications.org/cgi/content/full/peds.2004-0058v1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

